{"tid":1813501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防護中心：多5人到武漢後不適累積個案增至21宗","createTime":"2020-01-06T10:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T10:23:03.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c429ca9b5f67ad65c28516ff7f488c482d218330","tid":1813501,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"衛生防護中心截止中午，再收到5宗曾到湖北武漢返港後不適個案，累積個案增至21宗，新增的個案病發前無去過武漢的濕街市，全部情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n武漢的不明原因肺炎病例，增至59宗，但病情嚴重的個案減少至7宗。中文大學醫學院呼吸系統學講座教授許樹昌說，病毒是否能夠人傳人，仍言之尚早。。至今累積個案增至21宗，其中7人已出院。新增個案年齡2至65歲，病發前無去過武漢的濕街市，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1246130&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1246130%26csid%3D261_341&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=debf6571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1246130&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b0a86f2735816999213f00991e7f0d220c05d18d","tid":1813501,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"無事既<br />\n有人話佢老豆老母係醫生 唔會人傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c000a3fbf38c74a6cda04290890c54f0941a628","tid":1813501,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"屌你封關未呀垃圾政府"},{"pid":"2ade81baf2211ba66ddce707648e2b02a95e2e70","tid":1813501,"uid":151926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n個個去過武漢都拿野<br />\n武漢嗰邊最少超過一半人拿左野<br />\n中共仲話得5x宗<br />\n講少左1000倍"},{"pid":"1fea7a71b4bef20fe86e393a6967b378a6f69b66","tid":1813501,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a21f32facee96d42cccf01c84adc56402b946b0","tid":1813501,"uid":126382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202